        7
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matlacha%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "County Road 78 crosses Matlacha Pass, leading southwest to Pine Island Center and northeast through Cape Coral to North Fort Myers.",
